CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper May 9, 1959, pg. 13, reads: "Guidance Meet Leaders - Prior to the hour set for the beginning of the local Urban League's co-sponsored Guidance Conference at Westinghouse High School, last week, three of the principals held and informal chat.  Left to right: Richard S. Dowdy Jr., director of Industrial Relations, Urban League; G. Raymond Zimmerman, staff assistant, Plant Training Activities, U, S, Steel Corporation, and Dr. Paul E, Felton, principal of Westinghouse High School. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Urban League executive Richard S. Dowdy Jr., U. S. Steel executive G. Raymond Zimmerman, and Westinghouse High School principal Paul E. Felton, posed in Westinghouse High School
